\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5703f413b22918d6211e5b6130b85e2cfbbddff","tid":352191,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>習近平一定會打一次中小規模的戰爭，大規模先一定唔敢</blockquote><br />\n戰爭既規模唔係人可以控制到既, WW 從來都係諗住打中小規模, 點知打打下變左WW</blockquote><br />\n咁中印兩國的領導人，都唔似威廉國王/希特拉呢D痴線佬。</blockquote><br />\n你支那主子一郁手<br />\n大把國家就有藉口插手做鳩你支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好反省下點解你地支那種咁犯賤咁神憎鬼厭啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪又係利益交換，你真係以為全世界都圍堵中國咩。<br />\n<br />\n中國係美國規劃的世界格局中的其中一極，第一島鏈以內都被分配俾中國。<br />\n<br />\n習近平知道西方的底線係邊，同印度打仗。<br />\n<br />\n西方國家一定調停為主，絕對唔會幫印度出兵攻打中國。"},{"pid":"f8fe693c5810e17971f4009f58e6b88ee03a6408","tid":352191,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>習近平一定會打一次中小規模的戰爭，大規模先一定唔敢</blockquote><br />\n戰爭既規模唔係人可以控制到既, WW 從來都係諗住打中小規模, 點知打打下變左WW</blockquote><br />\n咁中印兩國的領導人，都唔似威廉國王/希特拉呢D痴線佬。</blockquote><br />\n你支那主子一郁手<br />\n大把國家就有藉口插手做鳩你支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好反省下點解你地支那種咁犯賤咁神憎鬼厭啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr